    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/3f85eb5300f24cf695c53f198fe3a968.webp?t=1772008063\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/3f85eb5300f24cf695c53f198fe3a968.poster.avif?t=1772008063\" class=\"bb_img\" width=694 height=428 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/912cdd7691c43945c99205f35868ac57.poster.avif?t=1772008063\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/912cdd7691c43945c99205f35868ac57.webm?t=1772008063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/912cdd7691c43945c99205f35868ac57.mp4?t=1772008063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >走进现代的类银河恶魔城世界，踏上经典味道十足的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将化身神秘少年希拉，为对抗远古代神明而生。《陨世之泪：涅槃》巧妙融合了经典JRPG的情感叙事和队伍构筑与类银河恶魔城的自由探索元素，外加一点类Rogue的挑战。每一次死亡都是成长，每一段友谊都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>献给JRPG的一封情书，以手绘风类银河恶魔城的形式呈现</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/995316fd0adee57294d109307e05366c.poster.avif?t=1772008063\" width=800 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/995316fd0adee57294d109307e05366c.webm?t=1772008063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446900/extras/995316fd0adee57294d109307e05366c.mp4?t=1772008063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索错综复杂的庞大世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越葱郁森林、失落古城与被历史尘封的遗迹，每一个地方都是人工创作，藏着许多秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗系统有深度，策略与操作并重</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精准闪避、完美格挡、武器切换。在战斗中活用队友的命定之友技能，实时调整策略，扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招募同伴，结成契友</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16个角色全程英文配音，灵感源自RPG经典职业——法师、剑士、诡术师、治疗师。缔结友谊，解锁组合技，一路升级你的队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >类Rogue机制，永久保留成长进度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都会有新的发现，比如地图的路线、敌人的套路、隐藏的机制。不过剧情进展、角色成长与升级项目不会因为一局结束而重置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你自己的城堡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的城堡不仅是庇护所，它的外观也会直观反映你的选择以及你与其他角色的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D手绘动画风美术</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >汲取了JRPG黄金时代佳作的灵感，以现代独立游戏笔触重新演绎，为你呈现精美的2D角色与场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否曾想象过《最终幻想》与《空洞骑士》融合在手绘风格世界会是什么样子？那个美好的想象，如今变成了现实。<br><br>其乐ID为： 陨世之泪：涅槃</p>",
